  "description": "Synthetic V&V 40 credibility package for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass conditions. Targets defeater W-AR-05: the primary validation result omits a comparedAgainst link; a secondary result carries a comparator drawn from ventricular-assist-device (VAD) operating conditions rather than CPB operating conditions, introducing an inference-method mismatch relative to the declared COU.",
